ment results on five\ndatasets show that the proposed framework has superior performance in\ndiscovering activities compared to the other state-of-the-art methods and has\nincreased accuracy of at least 4% on average.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 06:28:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 May 2022 04:46:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2022 02:17:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 09:25:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
