n these devices against malicious exploitation\nconsequently preserving privacy. This paper includes design considerations,\ncommand and control structures, characteristics, capabilities, intrusion, and\nother related work. Furthermore, proof of concept Botnet is implemented and\nexplained using the developed framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 11:26:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-17"}
